<h2>FAQ deep dives</h2>
<p><strong>Best stack for Shopify winback?</strong> Klaviyo/Drip segmentation by RFM and sensitivity, Sequenzy three-touch execution with suppressions, Yotpo proof email two, Postscript SMS for high-LTV only, Marsello points for VIP branch. Stack operators should document this answer in internal runbooks — not rely on tribal knowledge when agencies turn over.</p>
